OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fdispersing this morning. Otherwise a
OL,7,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine
OL,8,Falthough high cloud spilling across
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Warm, but cooler along
OL,10,Fthe east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,13,Fwith showery rain gradually spreading
OL,14,Fnortheast. Remaining cloudy overnight
OL,15,Fwith further showery rain extending
OL,16,Fnorthwards across most parts, perhaps
OL,17,Fbriefly heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
