OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Fscattered showers, these mainly in the
OL,7,Fmorning before it turns drier in the
OL,8,Fafternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCooler
OL,11,Fand cloudy over the weekend with
OL,12,Fshowers, these most widespread on
OL,13,FSaturday. Mainly dry on Monday with
OL,14,Fjust a few light showers.
